<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fund-Raise Insights — The Fundraising Intelligence Knowledge Base</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Deep dives into donor analytics, retention strategies, and the tools that help foundations raise more with less effort.">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/fund-raise-icon-flat.svg">
    <link href="/css/landing.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
    .ins-hero{padding:calc(80px + var(--banner-h, 40px)) 0 60px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1628 0%,#1A223D 50%,#3434D6 100%);color:#fff}
    .ins-hero h1{font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,44px);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:-0.5px}
    .ins-hero h1 span{color:#0D8CFF}
    .ins-hero p{font-size:clamp(14px,2vw,18px);opacity:.8;max-width:560px;margin:0;line-height:1.6}
    .ins-badge{display:inline-block;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;background:rgba(13,140,255,.15);color:#0D8CFF;margin-bottom:16px}
    .ins-container{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 20px 80px}
    .ins-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(380px,1fr));gap:32px}
    .ins-card{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s,transform .2s}
    .ins-card:hover{box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);transform:translateY(-2px)}
    .ins-card-img{height:220px;background:#f1f5f9;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden}
    .ins-card-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
    .ins-card-body{padding:24px}
    .ins-card-tag{display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:10px}
    .ins-tag-analytics{background:#E8F4FC;color:#3434D6}
    .ins-tag-retention{background:#FCEBEB;color:#dc2626}
    .ins-tag-strategy{background:#EAF3DE;color:#16a34a}
    .ins-tag-howto{background:#FFF6E0;color:#d97706}
    .ins-card-title{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.3}
    .ins-card-excerpt{font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 16px}
    .ins-card-meta{font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .ins-card-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#3434D6;text-decoration:none}
    .ins-card-link:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    .ins-cta{background:#f8fafc;border-radius:16px;padding:48px;text-align:center;margin-top:64px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb}
    .ins-cta h2{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin:0 0 8px}
    .ins-cta p{font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 24px;max-width:480px;display:inline-block}
    .ins-cta-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:12px 28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3434D6,#1A223D);color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}
    .ins-cta-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(52,52,214,.3)}
    /* LYBUNT mockup card */
    .ins-mockup{background:#1a2332;border-radius:10px;padding:20px;color:#fff;font-size:12px}
    .ins-mockup-dots{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:14px}
    .ins-mockup-dots span{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}
    .ins-mockup-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:14px;color:#94a3b8}
    .ins-mockup-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px}
    .ins-mockup-kpi{background:#243044;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 12px}
    .ins-mockup-kpi-label{font-size:10px;color:#64748b;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:2px}
    .ins-mockup-kpi-val{font-size:18px;font-weight:700}
    .ins-mockup-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #2d3a4d;font-size:11px}
    .ins-mockup-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
    @media(max-width:600px){.ins-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.ins-hero{padding:calc(70px + var(--banner-h, 40px)) 0 40px}.ins-cta{padding:32px 20px}}
    </style>
</head>
<body class="landing-page">

<%- include('banner') %>

<!-- ════════════════ NAV ════════════════ -->
<nav class="landing-nav" id="landing-nav">
    <div class="landing-nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="landing-nav-brand">
            <svg class="landing-nav-brand-icon" viewBox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28">
                <rect x="80" y="224" width="96" height="224" rx="20" fill="#3434D6"/>
                <rect x="208" y="112" width="96" height="336" rx="20" fill="#1A223D"/>
                <rect x="336" y="0" width="96" height="448" rx="20" fill="#0D8CFF"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="landing-nav-brand-text">Fund-Raise</span>
        </a>
        <div class="landing-nav-links" id="nav-links">
            <a href="/#replaces">Why Fund-Raise</a>
            <a href="/#dashboards">Dashboards</a>
            <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
            <a href="/whats-new">What's New</a>
            <a href="/insights" style="color:#0D8CFF;">Insights</a>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-nav-cta">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-nav-secondary">Sign In</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-nav-primary">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <button class="landing-nav-hamburger" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.getElementById('nav-links').classList.toggle('open');this.classList.toggle('open')">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- ════════════════ HERO ════════════════ -->
<section class="ins-hero">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="ins-badge">FUND-RAISE INSIGHTS</div>
        <h1>The fundraising intelligence <span>knowledge base.</span></h1>
        <p>Deep dives into donor analytics, retention strategies, and the tools that help foundations raise more with less effort.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════════ ARTICLES ════════════════ -->
<div class="ins-container">
    <div class="ins-grid">

        <!-- Article: LYBUNT / SYBUNT -->
        <article class="ins-card">
            <div class="ins-card-img">
                <div class="ins-mockup" style="margin:16px;width:calc(100% - 32px);">
                    <div class="ins-mockup-dots"><span style="background:#ff5f57"></span><span style="background:#febc2e"></span><span style="background:#28c840"></span></div>
                    <div class="ins-mockup-title">LYBUNT / SYBUNT Report</div>
                    <div class="ins-mockup-grid">
                        <div class="ins-mockup-kpi"><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-label">LYBUNT DONORS</div><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-val" style="color:#dc2626;">247</div></div>
                        <div class="ins-mockup-kpi"><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-label">SYBUNT DONORS</div><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-val" style="color:#d97706;">89</div></div>
                        <div class="ins-mockup-kpi"><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-label">REVENUE AT RISK</div><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-val" style="color:#0D8CFF;">$574K</div></div>
                        <div class="ins-mockup-kpi"><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-label">AVG PER DONOR</div><div class="ins-mockup-kpi-val">$1,708</div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ins-mockup-row"><span>RBC Foundation</span><span style="color:#dc2626;font-weight:600;">LYBUNT</span><span>$25,000</span></div>
                    <div class="ins-mockup-row"><span>Margaret Wilson</span><span style="color:#dc2626;font-weight:600;">LYBUNT</span><span>$15,000</span></div>
                    <div class="ins-mockup-row"><span>David Chen</span><span style="color:#d97706;font-weight:600;">SYBUNT</span><span>$5,000</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ins-card-body">
                <span class="ins-card-tag ins-tag-analytics">DONOR ANALYTICS</span>
                <h2 class="ins-card-title">What is a LYBUNT / SYBUNT Report?</h2>
                <p class="ins-card-excerpt">LYBUNT and SYBUNT reports identify lapsed donors before it's too late. Learn how to use them to recover at-risk revenue and strengthen your donor retention strategy.</p>
                <div class="ins-card-meta">
                    <span>April 6, 2025</span>
                    <span>&middot;</span>
                    <span>8 min read</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article: Donor Retention -->
        <article class="ins-card">
            <div class="ins-card-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FCEBEB,#FFF6E0);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
                <div style="text-align:center;padding:24px;">
                    <div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:8px;">&#128200;</div>
                    <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;">Retention Rate</div>
                    <div style="font-size:40px;font-weight:800;color:#dc2626;margin:8px 0;">45%</div>
                    <div style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;">Industry average &mdash; can you beat it?</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ins-card-body">
                <span class="ins-card-tag ins-tag-retention">RETENTION</span>
                <h2 class="ins-card-title">Why Donor Retention Matters More Than Acquisition</h2>
                <p class="ins-card-excerpt">Acquiring a new donor costs 5&ndash;10x more than retaining an existing one. Here's how to shift your strategy from volume to loyalty and see immediate ROI.</p>
                <div class="ins-card-meta">
                    <span>Coming soon</span>
                    <span>&middot;</span>
                    <span>6 min read</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="ins-cta">
        <h2>Stay ahead of the curve</h2>
        <p>New insights on donor analytics, fundraising strategy, and platform updates &mdash; delivered when they matter.</p>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="ins-cta-btn">Get Started with Fund-Raise &rarr;</a>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('../landing/footer') %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
<script>
// Sticky nav scroll effect
window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
    var nav = document.getElementById('landing-nav');
    if (nav) nav.classList.toggle('nav-scrolled', window.scrollY > 10);
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
